===Dictionary notes=== [[Category:Dictionary notes]]
*'''American Heritage Dictionary''' (via answers.com) lists unaccented spelling before the accented spelling.
*'''Collins Word Exchange''' has no entry for the accented spelling and does not include it in its article for the unaccented spelling.
*'''Merriam-Webster Online''' lists the accented spelling as a variant in their noun and verb entries but not in their adjective entry.
*'''MSN Encarta Dictionary''' redirects from any accented spelling (even incorrect ones) to the entry for the unaccented spelling. That entry does not mention the accented spelling.

